le.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27de92770f55da801900aa9d847fdee412b3606a","tid":2334104,"uid":133680,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T09:18:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b90b0e7acbfe8eb0aec7b9f3ee121a0ae5994166","tid":2334104,"uid":48234,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"27de92770f55da801900aa9d847fdee412b3606a","tid":2334104,"uid":133680,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T09:18:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T09:20:45.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">連登日報&mdash;支持獨裁政權者，無權享有言論自由<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1180589\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1180589</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/emWjmNa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FemWjmNa.jpg&h=c08f65f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n請問沙皮狗(狗隻#133680)你屙尿嗰陣起左腳定右腳?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1863914\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1863914</a><br />\n無恥沙皮狗(狗隻#133680)肯向香港手足道歉未?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2252543\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2252543</a><br />\n<br />\n最近沙皮狗經常違反板規證據:<br />\n沙皮狗請回應 有冇報章轉載權； 請LIHKG嚴肅跟進#133680侵犯版權問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2194433\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2194433</a><br />\n<br />\n擁有分身證據:<br />\n舉報會員老鳳(#48234)開分身及不停洗版<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/qatBJRX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/qatBJRX</a><br />\n喺佢自己惡意舉報post表示老鳳俾佢迫到傻咗,但係忘記切換帳號<br />\n而且俾佢特別置頂,等同明確承認開分身 R730(狗隻#137604)<br />\n<br />\n老鳳宣佈沙皮狗係終極奶共狗，必須將佢成個集團所有分身清除，否則連登必死<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2123735\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2123735</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3KfmK5D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3KfmK5D.jpg&h=2b495cb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XcpCtDj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXcpCtDj.png&h=d95fea7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yaEZGYj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyaEZGYj.png&h=6e12e1df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/j8uMrdt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fj8uMrdt.png&h=9e16340d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n沙皮狗一吠，所有連登手足便都指著牠笑，有的叫道，「沙皮狗，站務台又見到你罪證了！」他不回答，自言自語，「老鳳洗板，舉報佢開分身。」便開post亂鳩咁屈。他們又故意的高聲嚷道，「你一定又開了奶共的post了！」沙皮狗睜大眼睛吠，「你怎麼這樣憑空污狗清白&hellip;&hellip;」「什麼清白？我前天親眼見你開了奶共post，被追擊。」沙皮狗便漲紅了臉，額上的青筋條條綻出，爭辯吠，「文匯大公不能算奶共&hellip;&hellip;文匯大公！&hellip;&hellip;文匯大公報的事，能算奶共麼？」接連便是難懂的嗚咽聲，什麼「老鳳推人去死」，什麼「老鳳俾我迫到傻咗」之類，引得眾人都鬨笑起來：連登內外充滿了快活的空氣。</span></span>"},{"pid":"c84624146986b289f03cd3ee794a42324829b5db","tid":2334104,"uid":21757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T09:24:02.000Z","msg":"對"},{"pid":"8dfbacabb8ffd1893748b75751b440c3dbad4a2e","tid":2334104,"uid":310914,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T11:34:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6531065f65b3ba2010967d89520107e737dd8850","tid":2334104,"uid":24133,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c44ec8da76c41e0a509ec62fdcab15832f1ea4a6","tid":2334104,"uid":48234,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5ae913eacc5a54b7783b531152c7b561957fe2e8","tid":2334104,"uid":310914,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"01e193082e9fbd368ac4eaa37e8fd2b44c61f15e","tid":2334104,"uid":48234,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T04:08:14.000Z","msg":"嗰班仆街日鳩日話呢度cctoy<br />\n你咪撚跟啦<br />\n根本用呢個詞同自認係狗幾乎冇分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T04:09:10.000Z","msg":"懶寫多幾隻字咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T04:11:24.000Z","msg":"唔撚識打字? 時事台三隻字有幾難打?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20